content.title: NFTs are now in Ledger!
content.text: You can now manage, view, store, and enjoy your NFTs from your Ethereum accounts on Ledger Live. If you are already a Ledger Nano X user, you can even send your NFTs securely, without any blind signing. All you have to do is to make sure to update your Ledger Live app.

content.title: Manage your SOL in Ledger Live!
content.text: You can now create a Solana account, buy, send, and receive SOL in your Ledger Live app. All this while enjoying the security of your Ledger device.
